23050f5a2fbf1d0ad4ca1ee69986e6bf3bf33320.query:
SELECT videos.id, videos.title, videos.description, videos.path, videos.published_at, videos.duration, videos.channel_id,
                                         channels.title AS channel_title,
                                         playstates.id as "playstate_id?", playstates.position as "playstate_position?", playstates.modified_at as "playstate_modified_at?"
                                         FROM videos
                                         INNER JOIN channels ON channels.id = videos.channel_id
                                         LEFT JOIN playstates ON playstates.id = videos.id
                                         WHERE videos.id = $1

2db29f5476ab19bb6d781ebbce74b8c975c78246.query:
SELECT playstates.id, playstates.position, playstates.modified_at
                                         FROM playstates
                                         WHERE playstates.id = $1

af9d0a015ee78332f08f615229f802dcad7442d9.query:
INSERT INTO playlists
                 (title, slug)
                 VALUES
                 ($1, $2)
                 ON CONFLICT(slug) DO UPDATE SET title=$1
                 RETURNING id

b54e4d2bf99022a7922d80e1a486ea42c39d1cf5.query:
SELECT videos.id, videos.title, videos.description, videos.path, videos.published_at, videos.duration, videos.channel_id,
                                         channels.title AS channel_title,
                                         playstates.id as "playstate_id?", playstates.position as "playstate_position?", playstates.modified_at as "playstate_modified_at?"
                                         FROM videos
                                         INNER JOIN channels ON channels.id = videos.channel_id
                                         LEFT JOIN playstates ON playstates.id = videos.id
                                         WHERE videos.channel_id = $1

b728c47950aa43162ed4fc0e36e6b10f58d49db4.query:

                 (id, title, description, path, published_at, channel_id, duration)
                 VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
                 ON CONFLICT(id) DO UPDATE SET title=$2,description=$3,path=$4, published_at=$5,channel_id=$6,duration=$7

f12e9b0eaa9ba4351abb6f8cb1ee31364083229e.query:
SELECT videos.id, videos.title, videos.description, videos.path, videos.published_at, videos.duration, videos.channel_id,
                                         channels.title AS channel_title,
                                         playstates.id as "playstate_id?", playstates.position as "playstate_position?", playstates.modified_at as "playstate_modified_at?"
                                         FROM videos
                                         LEFT JOIN playstates ON videos.id = playstates.id
                                         INNER JOIN channels ON channels.id = videos.channel_id
                                         ORDER BY published_at DESC

f1eefec8099af66663f5f46080ab707f3d0a84d1.query:
SELECT videos.id as video_id, videos.title as video_title, videos.description as video_description, videos.path as video_path, videos.published_at as video_published_at, videos.duration as video_duration, videos.channel_id as channel_id,
                                         channels.title AS channel_title,
                                         playstates.id as "playstate_id?", playstates.position as "playstate_position?", playstates.modified_at as "playstate_modified_at?"
                                         FROM playlist_items
                                         INNER JOIN videos ON videos.id = playlist_items.video_id
                                         INNER JOIN channels ON channels.id = videos.channel_id
                                         LEFT JOIN playstates ON playstates.id = videos.id
                                         WHERE playlist_items.playlist_id = $1
                                         ORDER BY playlist_items.item_index ASC
